OL,3,CWidow calls for law change after
OL,4,Chusband's brain tumour death
OL,6,FA woman is calling for the law to
OL,7,Fchange to end what she calls a
OL,8,Fpostcode lottery of care for brain
OL,9,Fcancer patients following the death of
OL,10,Fher husband.
OL,12,FEllie James' husband Owain died in
OL,13,F2024 from a type of brain tumour known
OL,14,Fas a glioblastoma.
OL,16,FHis death followed difficulties
OL,17,Faccessing personalised treatment
OL,18,Fbecause most of his tumour, removed
OL,19,Fduring brain surgery, was not frozen.
