OL,3,CWidow calls for law change after
OL,4,Chusband's brain tumour death
OL,6,FAfter the operation, the family raised
OL,7,Ffunds to get Mr James a personalised
OL,8,Ftreatment.
OL,10,FMrs James told the Press Association:
OL,11,F"What we didn't realise at the time
OL,12,Fwas to have that vaccine you needed to
OL,13,Fhave fresh frozen tumour tissue."
OL,15,FShe said that 6cm of the tumour was
OL,16,Fput in a chemical, which made it
OL,17,Funusable for the treatment.
OL,19,F"That meant that we only had a tiny
OL,20,Flittle bit of tissue that could be
OL,21,Fused to make this vaccine," she said.
