OL,3,CWidow calls for law change after
OL,4,Chusband's brain tumour death
OL,6,F"And the more tissue you've got for
OL,7,Fthe vaccine, the more vaccines you can
OL,8,Fget. But because he only had a little
OL,9,Fbit, he only had three vaccines, where
OL,10,Freally he should have had around 30."
OL,12,FAfter receiving the vaccines ` which
OL,13,Fcame after surgery, chemotherapy and
OL,14,Fradiotherapy ` a scan revealed that
OL,15,Fthe tumour had "completely regressed,
OL,16,Fit was completely gone," she said.
OL,18,F"It was an absolute miracle. He had
OL,19,Fnine months of clear scans, his
OL,20,Fquality of life was completely normal.
