OL,3,CWidow calls for law change after
OL,4,Chusband's brain tumour death
OL,6,F"And then, unfortunately, nine months
OL,7,Flater, his tumour did come back and we
OL,8,Fweren't able to get any more vaccine,
OL,9,Funfortunately, and he sadly passed
OL,10,Faway in June 2024.
OL,12,F"If we'd had those 30 vaccines at the
OL,13,Fbeginning, I fully believe probably
OL,14,Fwould still be here today.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
