OL,3,CWidow calls for law change after
OL,4,Chusband's brain tumour death
OL,6,F"The way tissue is stored post-surgery
OL,7,Fhas a critical impact, because there
OL,8,Fis a real risk that powerful
OL,9,Finformation is lost, closing down
OL,10,Fpathways to clinical trials and
OL,11,Finnovative treatments.
OL,13,F"We are calling on Government to
OL,14,Fensure that fresh-frozen tissue
OL,15,Fstorage is available in all possible
OL,16,Finstances around the UK.
OL,18,F"The technology is there ` let's use
OL,19,Fit to make a difference."
